channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: CFL’s Edmonton Elks Introduce New Third Jersey Ahead of 75th Anniversary Season
item.description: Tonal triangle pattern on shoulders represents evergreen forests in Northern Alberta and North Saskatchewan River valley; new logo based on team's original logo adorns sleeves

item.title: Utah Jazz Unveil New Uniforms With Two-Season Rollout
item.description: The Utah Jazz have unveiled four new uniforms as part of a two-season transition that will once again put mountains and the color purple at the forefront of their branding.
